replyContent: Hi! Interesting comment... Why would you want to exclude shallow earthquakes? The reason of the current option (to exclude quakes deeper than a given max depth) is that shallow quakes are much more significant for people (who live on the surface and might feel them),  In addition, deep quakes are only detected if they are relatively big.
